{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "第八回\"私情\"。马如龙夜探小婉住处，本想查探其私情线索，却在布幔后撞见邱凤城，尴尬逃离。途中大婉出现，赠药并与其同行。二人边走边谈，马如龙将撞见邱凤城的糗事和盘托出，大婉对其印象改观。通过对话揭示：碧玉夫人曾在寒梅谷为女儿选婿，沈红叶已死，邱凤城成为最大受益者。马如龙坚信邱凤城不是凶手，推断幕后黑手为秘密组织\"天杀\"——一个企图制造江湖火并、趁乱崛起的杀人组织。大婉透露她从马如龙醉后得知诸多内情。马如龙决定找邱凤城追问线索，但刚要行动，巷子两头已被七名黑衣人堵住去路，危机骤临。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "你要我死，我也要你死。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁呀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wan",
      "text": "是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你是谁？我怎么知道你是谁？你难道连个名字都没有。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "想不到马公子又来了，是不是怕我一个人晚上太寂寞，想来替邱凤城好好的照顾照顾我。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wan",
      "text": "我知道你并不寂寞，我只不过怕你被人捏死。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你跟我来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "坐。请坐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你为什么不坐。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wan",
      "text": "这位子，好像不是我坐的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你不坐，这里还有谁来坐。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wan",
      "text": "好像还有个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这屋里除了凤城外，只有你进来过，怎么还有别的人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这是解酒药，这是紫金锭，这是胃痛散，这是健胃整肠的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你把我当成什么？当成了药罐子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我知道你不是药罐子，是个酒坛子。可惜只不过是很小很小的一个，也装不下太多酒。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你的头痛不痛？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "不痛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "怎么会不痛？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为我一向不喜欢管别人的闲事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你看见那个小婉了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "什么怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她长得怎么样？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "长得很不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "既然她长得很不错，你的样子看起来为什么活像见了鬼一样？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "如果我真的见了鬼反倒好些。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你看见了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我看见了邱凤城。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "如果我是你，那时候我也会恨不得能找条地缝钻下去的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可是我想不通。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "什么事想不通？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "邱凤城明明知道是你去了，为什么要躲起来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "他们毕竟不是名正言顺的夫妻，像他那种出身的人，总难免会有很多顾虑，如果是我，说不定我也会躲起来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "想不到你居然很会替别人着想。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "本来你认为我是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "本来我认为你又骄傲，又自私，别人的死活，你根本不会放在心上。可是现在我已经知道我错了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他看见你之后，说了些什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "就因为他什么都没有说，我反而更难受。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你说了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "那时候我能说什么？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他有没有要把你抓去交给冯超凡的意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你也没有问他，那天你走了之后，寒梅谷又发生了些什么事？碧玉夫人是不是到那里去了？有没有选上他做女婿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我没有问。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "这些事你怎么会知道的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "当然是有人告诉我的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "谁告诉你的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "一个喝醉了酒的人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "这个喝醉了酒的人就是我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你总算还不太笨。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "其实碧玉夫人用不着再选了，沈红叶已经一命呜呼，你已经变成个人人喊打的过街老鼠，除了银枪公子邱凤城之外，还有谁配作碧玉山庄的女婿。碧玉夫人就算还想选，也没有什么好选的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "但是，他绝不会是凶手！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "因为他已经有了以生死相许的心上人，他根本就不想做碧玉山庄的女婿。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "其实我也觉得他绝不可能做出这种事，只不过，他既然不会是凶手，你也不是，凶手是谁呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "一定是天杀！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "天杀是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "天杀不是一个人，是个秘密的组织，是个杀人的组织。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他们为什么要做这种事？为什么要害你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "因为，他们要造成混乱。我们几家人如果火并起来，江湖中一定会变得混乱，他们就可以乘机崛起。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为那时候别的门户和家族，都已因这次火并而两败伤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "但是我绝对不会让这种情况真的发生。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你准备怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我一定要先把天杀的首脑找出来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你准备怎么找？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这个人一定知道你们四位公子那天要到寒梅谷去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他怎么知道的？除了你们四个人之外，还有谁知道这件事？你有没有把这件事告诉过别人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我没有，可是，邱凤城……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我一定要去问问他，有很多事都只有问他才会明白。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你是不是准备现在就去问他。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "当然现在就去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你真会选时候，现在去真是再好也没有了，现在他们说不定又在那里你捏死我，我捏死你，你及时赶去，正好又可以救他们一次，他们一定感激得要命。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你认为我应该什么时候去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你最好现在就去，快去。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你为什么又要我现在就去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为你现在不去，只怕就永远都去不成了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "现在你恐怕已经去不成了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    }
